{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"AgentSight","page":{"layout":"document","title":"AgentSight","description":"基于 eBPF 的 LLM 与 AI agent 零插桩可观测工具。","descriptionIsExcerpt":false,"bodyHtml":"<p>AgentSight 从系统边界观测 LLM 和 AI agent 行为。它把进程活动、TLS/网络流量、文件访问、工具执行和资源行为关联起来，不需要在 agent 应用里接入 SDK。</p>\n<p>当应用日志不够可信或不够完整时，可以使用 AgentSight：例如会执行子进程的 coding agent、调用远程 LLM API 的 CLI agent、多 agent workflow，或者需要审计证据的生产试点。</p>\n<p>项目链接：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>GitHub: <a href=\"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/agentsight\">https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/agentsight</a></li>\n<li>Paper: <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.02736\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.02736</a></li>\n<li>旧页面：<a href=\"/GPTtrace/agentsight/\">/GPTtrace/agentsight/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"能捕获什么\">能捕获什么</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>在支持的 TLS 库路径上，捕获加密前的 LLM API 请求与响应。</li>\n<li>进程树、子进程执行、命令参数和生命周期事件。</li>\n<li>与 agent 行为相关的文件读写和元数据事件。</li>\n<li>可与进程活动关联的网络和 HTTP 信号。</li>\n<li>用于回放 agent session 的运行时指标和事件时间线。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"为什么在系统层观测\">为什么在系统层观测</h2>\n<p>应用层 tracing 只能看到应用主动上报的内容。AgentSight 位于应用之下，更适合观察 closed-source 工具、agent 子进程、shell 命令，以及绕过框架插桩的提示词、工具调用或文件访问。</p>\n<p>AgentSight 不是要替代应用层 tracing，而是补足 LangSmith、OpenTelemetry、proxy 日志或自定义 SDK 之外的 ground-truth 层。</p>\n<h2 id=\"文档\">文档</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/agentsight/quickstart/\">快速开始</a>：安装二进制，记录 Claude Code、Gemini CLI 或 Python agent，并打开 UI。</li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/agentsight/architecture/\">架构</a>：eBPF probe、Rust collector、analyzer、存储和 UI 如何协作。</li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/agentsight/visualization/\">可视化</a>：如何阅读进程树、事件时间线、日志视图和指标。</li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/agentsight/operational-notes/\">运行说明</a>：权限、隐私、支持环境和部署建议。</li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/agentsight/troubleshooting/\">故障排查</a>：事件缺失或 TLS hook 挂载失败时的常见原因。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"最小流程\">最小流程</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">wget</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/agentsight/releases/download/v0.1.1/agentsight</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">chmod</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> +x</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> agentsight</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># 记录 Claude Code。</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> claude</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># 记录 Gemini CLI；它通常以 node 进程运行。</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> node</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># 记录 Python AI 工具。</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./agentsight</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> record</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -c</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> python</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>然后打开 <a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080\">http://127.0.0.1:8080</a> 查看捕获到的 session。</p>\n<h2 id=\"当前范围\">当前范围</h2>\n<p>AgentSight 主要面向 Linux agent 进程，以及常见 userspace TLS 和进程可观测路径。它提供证据和可见性；策略执行、sandbox 和 runtime guardrail 应交给 ActPlane 或其他专门的安全控制层。</p>","headings":[{"id":"能捕获什么","text":"能捕获什么","depth":2},{"id":"为什么在系统层观测","text":"为什么在系统层观测","depth":2},{"id":"文档","text":"文档","depth":2},{"id":"最小流程","text":"最小流程","depth":2},{"id":"当前范围","text":"当前范围","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/agentsight/index.zh.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-06-02T03:15:25.000Z","createdAt":"2026-06-02T03:15:25.000Z","authors":[{"name":"LinuxDev9002","email":"linuxdev8883@example.com"}]},"path":"/zh/agentsight/","alternates":{"en":"/agentsight/","zh":"/zh/agentsight/"},"continuation":{"previous":{"title":"AgentSight 架构","description":"从 eBPF probe 到分析、存储和可视化的数据路径。","href":"/zh/agentsight/architecture/"},"next":{"title":"AgentSight 运行说明","description":"AgentSight 的权限、隐私、支持环境和部署建议。","href":"/zh/agentsight/operational-notes/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"AgentSight","items":[{"title":"总览","href":"/zh/agentsight/"},{"title":"快速开始","href":"/zh/agentsight/quickstart/"},{"title":"架构","href":"/zh/agentsight/architecture/"},{"title":"可视化","href":"/zh/agentsight/visualization/"},{"title":"运行说明","href":"/zh/agentsight/operational-notes/"},{"title":"故障排查","href":"/zh/agentsight/troubleshooting/"}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}